{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|1}} And it shall come to pass, when all these things are come upon thee, the blessing and the curse, which I have set before thee,

{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|2}} And thou shalt call them to mind among all the nations, whither the LORD thy God hath driven thee,

{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|3}} And shalt return unto the LORD thy God, and shalt obey his voice according to all that I command thee this day,

